We need assistance from the L3 team regarding a $49 Premium plan MCSL customer.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
The customer has generated 1000+ labels and has requested an order report for the period August 1 – August 31, 2025.
&nbsp;
Could you please share the order report for August 2025?
&nbsp;
Additionally, if possible, could you please enable the Order Report feature for the following store?
&nbsp;
Store Details:
  Store URL: agro-coffee.myshopify.com   Account ID: 2d8bd666-ea7e-48b6-bca7-2dd550306af5

Hello Zac,
&nbsp;
We have enabled a feature for your store where you can export an order report and check for the details of the orders processed. Click on Export, Select the Date Range, provide the email ID for which the report to be shared and click on Export Orders.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
Please give this a try and check if it works.
&nbsp;

&nbsp;
Thanks and Regards,
Sagar K S
Team PluginHive

Good morning, Sagar! 
  Thank you very much for enabling that in our account!&nbsp;  
  It works brilliantly, we have Province, Zip code and Street address in the .csv, but would it be possible to also add City/Town?&nbsp;  We're trying to assess how we can better serve remote locations within BC and beyond.&nbsp;  
  Thank you!  Zac

Hello Zac,
